gn=right> <br> <a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm8.showMessage?topicID=193.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/finnoruukserverfrm8.showMessage?topicID=194.topic"> Next Topic >> </a> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=95%><tr><td bgcolor=#FFFFFF><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=5 cellspacing=1><tr><td valign=top bgcolor=#333366 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Author</font></td><td valign=top bgcolor=#333366 class=headings><font color=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ubalanthor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Balanthor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dubious Poster</span><br>  Posts: 172<br> <font color=#778899>(12/1/01 10:35:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_thumbsdown.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: &quot;Mother Earth&quot; == oxymoron</span><hr size=1> <br>
